Environment
Team Productivity Environment Restricted

Overview
The B2B2C - Promo Decoupling Flow creates and saves the weekly B2B2C Promo Decoupling files to a secure Sharepoint Online repository, created purely for this process.

For more info on the Promo Decoupling process, see 
B2B2C Promo Decoupling
.

Schedule/Trigger
Flow is triggered based on when there is any new file added or modified to the folder ‘/b2b2c-transaction-files/Output Files/Status’.

This Flow was designed to be used in conjunction with Snowflake task; COL_DB.COL_DM.B2B2C_PROMO_DECOUPLING. This task is run weekly (Thursday @ 11am) and it performs the data query that extracts the relevant data for the promotional week (Wednesday - Tuesday). The final step of this task is to update the file: b2b2c-transaction-files/Output Files/Status/Promo_Decoupling_Status.csv. 

Therefore once the Promo Decoupling Snowflake task is executed (and successfully run) this flow is automatically kick started. For more info on the B2B2C_Promo_Decoupling task, see 
Promo Decoupling - Technical Documentation.

